# üåå AI-Backend Sprint: 12 Days to Intelligence

> **Project Codename:** Cosmonyx-AI-Core
> **Objective:** Transitioning from deterministic `if/else` logic to probabilistic AI-driven backend systems.

This repository serves as a technical log and codebase for a 12-day intensive sprint into AI Engineering, specifically tailored for a Python-centric backend stack (Django/Flask/AWS).

---

## üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack

* **Language:** Python 3.11+
* **AI Orchestration:** OpenAI API / Anthropic / AWS Bedrock
* **Vector Infrastructure:** ChromaDB (Local) / Pinecone (Cloud)
* **Backend Frameworks:** Flask (for microservices) / Django (for full-stack)
* **Infrastructure:** Docker (Optimized Multi-stage builds)

